title: DPS-BEST OF- Sep 18, 2020

description:
On Today's Episode of the Dan Patrick Show we spoke to an SNL Alum, an NBA player in the Bubble, a Super Bowl winning QB and the Commissioner of a Power 5 Conference, not all in that order though. Larry Scott Pac12 Commissioner, Russelll Wilson Seahawaks QB, Heat Forward Duncan Robinson and Actor/Comedian Kevin Nealon all joined the program. Plus we recap all the action from last night's Bengals/Browns game.
